Laila Morse https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laila_Morse 0 Maureen "Mo" Oldman (born 1 August 1945), known by her stage name Laila Morse, is an English actress. Her best known roles include Janet in drama film Nil by Mouth (1997) and Mo Harris in BBC One soap opera EastEnders (2000–2016, 2018–present).
